The Night I Made My Choice Of Life.<br>
She Came to me,This Goddess Of Wisdom.<br>
Through Words of Knowledge She Spoke.<br>
<br>
Here I offer thee a Rose Of Two Colors.<br>
It is Red as Passions of Love,That Poets Talk of.<br>
<br>
Yellow as a friendship born between two souls,<br>
<br>
If only the Second Hue is to Thy likeing,So be it,<br>
Such is Fate.<br>
<br>
It Shall Sufice to sate,My thirst for thy Presence.<br>
<br>
But just incase thy mind should ever shift,<br>
And you find thine Eyes,Longing for a touch of Crimson,<br>
<br>
You need only kiss the rose,and its Flame shall flair and Envelup us both.<br>
<br>
In a Fire I kindled here,In this Heart of Mine, Where I did Grow this Rose I offer Thee<br>
<br>
This Night Brought to Thy Mind,As a Dream formed by Her Line.<br>
A Goddesses Wish To Have This Warrior,She then Awoke To the Rose.<br>
Kissing its Petals Of Red. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.showMessage?topicID=10.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.showMessage?topicID=4.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.threadControl?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya">Sisters of Themiscrya<option value="amazonsunitefrm6">Amazons of the Norther